latestPosts.caption:
While wrapping up an incredible time at Alma Academy, my work journey took me to the stunning city of Dubrovnik, Croatia!

This was an amazing reminder of how my profession allows me to explore various parts of the world. 
This truly beautiful and serene place offered the perfect opportunity to relax and recharge amidst the hustle of a busy life. Absolutely captivated by every moment!

#almaacademy #travelprofessionally#drmalavikakohli #explorecroatia #workandwander #sereneescape #mumbaidermatologist #wanderlustmoments

The Alma Academy is not just an event—it’s a movement . 
An aesthetic moment that brings together brilliant minds from around the world, sharing groundbreaking case presentations and the best of Alma technologies. It’s where clinical excellence meets a human touch, shaping a more holistic aesthetic journey for every patient. 

I had the honour of presenting my results in treating acne scars using the Alma Harmony Pro XL platform—and the response was truly heartwarming. Grateful for the appreciation and the opportunity to contribute to such a prestigious platform.

Beyond the science of laser technologies and it’s healing piowet , it was equally enriching to engage with colleagues from across the globe—exchanging ideas, answering curious minds, and soaking in the medieval magic of Dubrovnik.
The Game of Thrones–themed evening, the city’s charm, and the Adriatic breeze were the perfect backdrop for both learning and unwinding.

Returned home recharged—with greater knowledge, deeper awareness, and fresh inspiration to serve my patients even better each day.

Thank you, Alma, for this truly enriching experience.

#malavikakohli #malavikakohliclinic #almaacademy #aestheticexcellence #globalcollaboration #laserhealing #patientcentriccare #innovativeaesthetics  #themedfun #gameofthronesevening

latestPosts.caption:
Honored to have been the Guest of Honor at the installation ceremony of the incoming President of the Vidarbha Dermatological Society (VDS), Dr. Asra Khumushi, and her dynamic team in Nagpur! 

It was inspiring to witness Dr. Asra's introduction to her tenure. I also had the opportunity to present on "Melasma Revisited" and be part of a very engaging and insightful panel discussion on hyperpigmentation with leading dermatologists from Vidarbha and Nagpur. 

A truly amazing feeling to share the dias with respected dignitaries Dr. Girish Gandhi, Mrs.Pragati Patil and others. Heartfelt congratulations to Dr. Asra, and wishing her and her fantastic team, including Dr. Priyanka Magia (Hon .Secretary,VDS ), a resounding success in the upcoming year!

#drmalavikakohli #vidarbhadermatology #drasrakhumushi #MelasmaRevisited #HyperpigmentationPanel #dermatologyleadership #nagpurevents #dermatologycommunity #inspiringleadership

Sharing my experience in injectables, detailing how to achieve predictable results by understanding the anatomy, science, and art of toxins, fillers, exosomes, NCTF, and nucleotides, alongside lasers and devices for a truly gratifying aesthetic journey for our patients. Congratulations to SARCD 2025 for an amazing sharing platform.
